## 099_Switches_Logic
# 12.12.2021 S-a adaugat regula "Logic when Sonoffmini3 turns on"
# 24.04.2022 s-au adaugat Items ScriptParrot_Sonoff1_up, ScriptParrot_Sonoff2_up, ScriptParrot_Sonoff3_up la reguli
# 2026-03-07 FIX4: priza1forceon now skips if Priza1_BatteryFull == ON, preventing
#            a rapid ON/OFF power cycle when the socket is turned on while the
#            battery is already full.
